org.qi4j.library.cxf
Class JaxWsServerFactoryInfo

java.lang.Object
  org.qi4j.library.cxf.JaxWsServerFactoryInfo

public final class JaxWsServerFactoryInfo
extends Object

The JaxWsServerFactoryInfo is a metaInfo type to set to services that wants to be exposed as WebServices. Additionally, the service must have a Visibility set to application otherwise the Apache CXF extension will not be able to detect the presence of the service (assuming it is in a higher layer).
